      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HI JESSIE (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 19 times for eight wins and six minors. Scored by 3 lengths last time (16.77) in a Free For All over 300m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. WILGUNYA KNIGHT (5) was strongly fancied last time and hit the ground running with a slick early split, giving a sight but could manage only second (17.11) at this track over 300m. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Expected to be in this for a long way. MALMSTEEN (2) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when second (17.27) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Can find the frame this time. KICKER SPLASH (7) was a winner two back and strongly fancied last time but could only manage fourth (17.15) at this track. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong.",
